!!!
%html
  %head
    %title Six Second Film Festival</title>
    %link{:href => 'http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Archivo+Narrow', :rel => 'stylesheet', :type => 'text/css'}
    %link{:href => 'http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cinzel:400', :rel => 'stylesheet', :type => 'text/css'}

    %meta{:content => "The film festival for people without patience", :name => "description"}

    = favicon_link_tag "favicon.ico" 
    = stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all"
    = javascript_include_tag "application"
    = csrf_meta_tags

  %body{:style => "font-size: 18px;"}
    .container.static_container{:style => "padding-top: 0px"}

      .logoHolder{:style => "margin: 10px 280px 40px 280px;"}
        .subtitle{:style => "margin-top:40px"} Official
        .main_title Six Second Film Festival
        .subtitle "for people without patience"

      %p Welcome to the Six Second Film Festival. Here's how to play:
      %p 
        %span Go to the app store and download Vine. 
        = image_tag("vine_icon.jpg", :style => "position:relative;top:7px;height:30px;width:30px;")

      %p 
        %span Every hour, 
        = image_tag("6.png", :style => "position:relative;top:9px;")
        %span will post a new festival subject. These subjects are available on the top line of the site, and by following @6secfilms on twitter.

      %p Your job is to make a short film using vine and post it to twitter with the hashtag of that hour's festival subject. 

      %p 
        %span The films with the most retweets one hour later get posted here
        = image_tag("6.png", :style => "position:relative;top:9px;")
        %span .

      %p For example, if the 3pm festival subject is "one of the characters must be a pirate" you have until 4pm to post your pirate movie with the hashtag #pirate6sf.

      %p
        = image_tag("pirate.png")

      %p At 5pm, all the vine movies on twitter with the hashtag #pirate6sf will be counted and the movies with the most retweets win. 

      %p Enjoy the show.
	    
      %p - 6SFF